    class Prisma,PG,Redis,TS,RS,CS,Multiplier dataStyle
    class ST,Gemini,Semrush externalStyle
    class ViteDev,Vitest,MSW,GH,Husky,Vercel,Railway,Supabase,Upstash infraStyle
